## Current Tables Created

### `track_relationships`
Track relationships for content derivation (checkpoints from articles, etc.)

```sql
CREATE TABLE track_relationships (
  id UUID PRIMARY KEY DEFAULT gen_random_uuid(),
  organization_id UUID NOT NULL,
  source_track_id UUID NOT NULL REFERENCES tracks(id) ON DELETE CASCADE,
  derived_track_id UUID NOT NULL REFERENCES tracks(id) ON DELETE CASCADE,
  relationship_type TEXT NOT NULL CHECK (relationship_type IN ('source', 'prerequisite', 'related')),
  created_at TIMESTAMP WITH TIME ZONE DEFAULT now(),
  UNIQUE(source_track_id, derived_track_id, relationship_type)
);

CREATE INDEX idx_track_relationships_source ON track_relationships(source_track_id);
CREATE INDEX idx_track_relationships_derived ON track_relationships(derived_track_id);
CREATE INDEX idx_track_relationships_org ON track_relationships(organization_id);
```
